<!-- index.njk -->
{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  {% set activePage = "faqs" %} 
  {% include "partials/navigation.njk" %}
  <main role="main" class="main main--faq">
    <div
    class="hero hero--small hero--faqs"
    title="Hero Image
                Services Cutting"
  >
    <div class='hero__title--center'>
      <h2
        class="hero__title hero__title--center-top"
      >
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>
      
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='about-info--grey'>
      <ul class="faq-list">
        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>What types of Metal do Acton Bright Steel stock?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span>
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">We stock over 2000 different sizes of freecutting, carbon &amp; alloy steels and is the largest range of bright steel steel stocked in the South of England. In addition, we also have a comprehensive range of stainless and tool steel. Over the last few years we have added aluminium, brass and tube, box section and sheet to provide a multi metal "one stop shop" service to many thousands of customers.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>Can you saw bars up into pieces for me?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span>
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">Yes, our fully automatic band saws enable us to offer a quick, accurate and competitive sawing service from 1 to 10,000 off. We also cut many of our bars in half or in three, to cater for individual customers bar feeds. Free issue cutting can also be undertaken.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>Can you chamfer bars for me?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span>
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">Yes, we can offer chamfering in-house up to 65mm diameter, whether it be for 3 metre lengths, 1 metre shafts or to your required length</p>
        </li>

        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>Are there any other services you can offer?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span>
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">Yes, our Sales Staff will be happy to advise you on Annealing, Precision Grinding, Crack Detection, Ultrasonic Testing and Degreasing.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>Do you deliver and how much would it cost?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span> 
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">We offer a next day service at no extra charge to the majority of the South of England, please call our Sales Team 01784 455273 for a quote and expected delivery time. Alternatively you can collect your order from our warehouse, conveniently located near junction 13 of the M25.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>How can I be sure of what I'm buying?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span>          
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">We have a comprehensive goods inward procedure through which all incoming materials are processed, before they are put into picking stock. We also operate a computerised stock control system which has been developed "in house" over many years which provides us with full batch traceability on all bars, sawn pieces and short ends.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>I need to have Certificates with my goods, can you help?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span>
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">We can supply goods with a Certificate of Conformity, Certificate of Analysis and with Mechanical Properties where applicable. Mill certificates can also be provided where available.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>Can you assist with foreign and old drawing specifications?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span>
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">Yes, our international specification comparison guide is available on the website and within our brochure. Our staff will also be happy to assist wherever possible with any other specifications from our extensive knowledge and library of specifications, which go back many years from the various different standards.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="faq-list__item">
          <p class="faq-list__item__title title--small title--white">
            <span class='faq-list__item__title__text'>Can I collect goods from you, and do you sell to the public?</span>
            <span class='show-hide-btn'></span>
          </p>
          <p class="faq-list__item__answer">Yes, we are open for collections Monday to Friday 9.00am - 5.00pm. We also accept cash, cheques and most major credit/debit cards.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
{% endblock %}